		<div class="entry-summary">
		
		<p>It &#8216;s still spring, friends, but I want you to mark your calendars now (and start saving your book money, because WOW).</p>
<p>Saturday, October 13th, 2018, from 10am to 4:30pm.<br />
Haverhill Public Library<br />
Haverhill, MA</p>
<p>Merrimack Valley Halloween Book Festival 2018 will feature at least more than SIXTY authors, artists, and filmmakers. Panel discussions. Brand new book debuts. And, of course, Trick or Treat candy.</p>
<p>But I know, I know&#8230;you want the list. Here it is. (*Asterisk denotes FIRST TIME attendees&#8230;and look at that list!) [There are a few more I&#8217; m   waiting   to   confirm.] </p>
